WEBVTT

00:03.934 --> 00:08.400
Subtitles: RaceMan
www.forom.com

00:16.067 --> 00:20.934
* Love and marriage *

00:20.969 --> 00:22.734
* Go together like *

00:22.769 --> 00:25.200
* A horse and carriage *

00:25.235 --> 00:29.200
* This I tell ya, brother *

00:29.235 --> 00:31.133
* You can't have one *

00:31.168 --> 00:34.033
* Without the other *

00:34.068 --> 00:38.934
* Love and marriage *

00:38.969 --> 00:40.334
* It's an institute *

00:40.369 --> 00:42.734
* You can't disparage *

00:42.769 --> 00:46.501
* Ask the local gentry *

00:46.536 --> 00:51.067
* And they will say
It's elementary *

00:51.102 --> 00:55.868
* Try, try, try
To separate them *

00:55.903 --> 00:59.567
* It's an illusion *

00:59.602 --> 01:04.700
* Try, try, try
And you will only come *

01:04.736 --> 01:08.133
* To this conclusion *

01:08.168 --> 01:10.234
* Love and marriage **

